scripts.name: Gitlab raw commit adder
scripts.description: Replace the mangled commit message with the full patch, which is in general more useful to the experienced git user than the web UI, where you have to change views multiple time to see the contents of a commit and it's impossible to get the raw patch (other than appending .patch to the URL).
